580
00:39:43,744 --> 00:39:44,992
♫ I saw it ♫

581
00:39:44,992 --> 00:39:47,456
♫ Twinkling in the darkness ♫

582
00:39:49,199 --> 00:39:51,520
It's much more lively here
than it was two years ago.

583
00:39:51,520 --> 00:39:53,960
Many shops on Linjiang Road have moved here.

584
00:39:53,960 --> 00:39:55,180
Those that haven't moved

585
00:39:55,180 --> 00:39:56,340
have all opened branches here.

586
00:39:56,340 --> 00:39:57,440
Xiaoman, you are back.

587
00:39:58,039 --> 00:39:59,120
Okay, you go ahead.

588
00:39:59,120 --> 00:40:00,128
I'm leaving.

589
00:40:01,599 --> 00:40:02,599
Have you gone to see Uncle?

590
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:06,840
He has a heart stent surgery in two days.

591
00:40:07,599 --> 00:40:09,079
Although the technology has advanced,

592
00:40:09,079 --> 00:40:10,800
I'm still a bit worried.

593
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:14,519
You have a lot on your mind.

594
00:40:15,199 --> 00:40:16,480
It's not just about that, right?

595
00:40:18,464 --> 00:40:19,520
The matter about the shares?

596
00:40:20,840 --> 00:40:24,000
Uncle asked me to hurry up
with the shareholding procedures.

597
00:40:24,519 --> 00:40:25,519
Isn't it a good thing?

598
00:40:26,719 --> 00:40:28,919
Isn't that what you've been saving money

599
00:40:28,919 --> 00:40:30,280
