600
00:40:33,519 --> 00:40:35,000
I lent the money to a friend.

601
00:40:36,679 --> 00:40:39,280
I wanted to tell him today,

602
00:40:41,239 --> 00:40:42,520
but seeing how happy he was,

603
00:40:42,520 --> 00:40:43,719
I couldn't tell him.

604
00:40:48,224 --> 00:40:49,248
How much is missing?

605
00:40:50,208 --> 00:40:51,280
More than 200,000.

606
00:40:51,872 --> 00:40:52,980
I'll lend you some.

607
00:40:52,980 --> 00:40:54,080
No need.

608
00:40:55,400 --> 00:40:57,239
It's not just about the money.

609
00:40:58,079 --> 00:40:59,400
What else are you worried about?

610
00:41:03,712 --> 00:41:04,832
Your Aunt?

611
00:41:08,519 --> 00:41:10,280
Why are you thinking so much?

612
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:11,880
These shares belong to Master,

613
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:12,880
and they should be yours.

614
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:14,880
Others can't meddle in your family affairs,

615
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:15,904
but they are all watching.

616
00:41:16,519 --> 00:41:18,480
How she treats you determines
what kind of person she is.

617
00:41:20,519 --> 00:41:21,960
If she can't figure it out at her age,

618
00:41:21,960 --> 00:41:23,140
she's not your Aunt then.

619
00:41:23,140 --> 00:41:24,400
Just rest assured.

620
